public interface ReplaceablePropertyChangeListener
extends java.beans.PropertyChangeListener

The listener interface for receiving notification of when an object is to be replaced by a different instance. Used for example by Modules when changes are held until the Apply button is pressed.

This code was developed by NASA, Goddard Space Flight Center, Code 588 for the Scientist's Expert Assistant (SEA) project.
